# Frappe / Docker local dev - vendored repo and runtime data, not our source
frappe_docker/*
apps/*
sites/*
logs/*
backups/*
!apps/.gitkeep
!sites/.gitkeep
!logs/.gitkeep
!backups/.gitkeep

# frappe_docker/ is a vendored clone (README, docs, apps/, images/, every
# compose variant we don't use) -- not worth tracking wholesale. But three
# files there are the actual configuration inputs for THIS deployment and
# exist nowhere else, so a fresh server setup has nothing to rebuild from
# without them: apps.json (which apps/branches get baked into the image),
# overrides.local/ (the edupro_sms bind-mount + shared bench-env volume
# fix -- see its own header comment for why this exists), and .env.example
# (a redacted template for the real .env, which stays gitignored via the
# blanket `.env` rule below). See docs/08_Deployment.md for how these
# combine into the actual running compose.edupro.yaml, which is NOT
# tracked here since it bakes in this machine's absolute bind-mount paths
# and current Docker bridge IP -- both need re-deriving per machine.
!frappe_docker/apps.json
!frappe_docker/.env.example
!frappe_docker/overrides.local

# apps/edupro_sms is OUR custom app -- the actual source code for every
# feature in this project. It was excluded by the apps/* rule above for
# the project's whole history; un-ignore it explicitly so it's finally
# version-controlled. (Other apps under apps/ -- frappe/erpnext/education
# -- are vendored inside the Docker image itself, never bind-mounted to
# the host, so apps/* still correctly excludes anything else that shows
# up there.)
!apps/edupro_sms

# One explicit, dated full-site backup (database + files), pushed on
# request as a disaster-recovery snapshot -- see docs/13_Backup_Restore.md.
# Contains real student/guardian PII and financial data; this is a
# deliberate one-off exception to the blanket backups/* rule above, not a
# standing policy. Future backups stay untracked unless individually
# un-ignored the same way -- don't broaden this to `!backups/*`.
!backups/20260712_013402-edupro_localhost-database.sql.gz
!backups/20260712_013402-edupro_localhost-files.tar
!backups/20260712_013402-edupro_localhost-private-files.tar
!backups/20260712_013402-edupro_localhost-site_config_backup.json

*.log
*.pid
.env

# Note: apps/edupro_sms/.gitignore (inside the app itself, from
# `bench new-app`) already excludes __pycache__/*.pyc/etc within it.

# Real staff login credentials (plaintext passwords) -- generated locally
# for handout, never committed. Regenerate via a fresh password reset if
# this file is lost; it's not a source-of-truth artifact.
Edupro_SMS_Staff_Login_Credentials.pdf

# Generated rosters containing real student names -- handout artifacts,
# regenerate from the database on demand rather than tracking in git.
Edupro_SMS_Lower6_Upper6_Combinations.pdf
Edupro_SMS_Lower6_Combinations_Template.pdf
